00:16:15.199 --> 00:16:20.110
everywhere.

00:16:22.240 --> 00:16:24.670
It was

00:16:24.680 --> 00:16:28.350
awful. The Lord said 350 million is a small

00:16:28.350 --> 00:16:28.360
number compared to

00:16:28.360 --> 00:16:30.189
what they have

00:16:30.199 --> 00:16:33.189
planned for

00:16:33.199 --> 00:16:37.749
North America.

00:16:49.680 --> 00:16:52.990
If you look

00:16:52.990 --> 00:16:53.000
at

00:16:53.000 --> 00:16:54.990
the Black Death,

00:16:57.120 --> 00:16:59.829
it took out

00:17:02.839 --> 00:17:05.110
almost half the

00:17:05.110 --> 00:17:05.120
population—50

00:17:05.120 --> 00:17:06.789
million people

00:17:11.640 --> 00:17:13.750
perished.

00:17:16.520 --> 00:17:19.069
The plan was to take out

00:17:19.079 --> 00:17:20.870
half.

00:17:23.390 --> 00:17:23.400
I

00:17:26.199 --> 00:17:29.430
saw

00:17:32.590 --> 00:17:32.600
Trump

00:17:36.600 --> 00:17:39.590
crying and asking for mercy

00:17:39.600 --> 00:17:42.909
for America.

00:17:45.760 --> 00:17:49.630
He was skinnier

00:17:49.630 --> 00:17:49.640
and

00:17:49.640 --> 00:17:54.070
looked

00:17:54.080 --> 00:17:58.830
very worn out, but he was broken

00:17:58.840 --> 00:18:00.350
to the point

00:18:00.350 --> 00:18:00.360
of

00:18:00.360 --> 00:18:04.110
interceding. I saw

00:18:04.120 --> 00:18:07.590
pastors in the Oval Office pacing and praying in the spirit with him. I

00:18:07.590 --> 00:18:07.600
saw

00:18:07.600 --> 00:18:10.750
a

00:18:10.750 --> 00:18:10.760
tall,

00:18:10.760 --> 00:18:13.669
slender

00:18:13.669 --> 00:18:13.679
pastor

00:18:13.679 --> 00:18:16.070
with

00:18:18.039 --> 00:18:19.950
a

00:18:24.909 --> 00:18:24.919
bald

00:18:31.110 --> 00:18:31.120
head—he

00:18:36.440 --> 00:18:39.110
was

00:18:39.110 --> 00:18:39.120
balder

00:18:39.120 --> 00:18:42.110
than

00:18:42.110 --> 00:18:42.120
me

00:18:42.120 --> 00:18:44.390
on

00:18:49.320 --> 00:18:51.830
top—praying

00:18:58.799 --> 00:19:00.789
in

00:19:09.240 --> 00:19:12.350
a gray suit. As they prayed, I saw shockwaves like paddles hitting a nation to wake it up. The blackness

00:19:12.350 --> 00:19:12.360
started to ripple away. Then I saw a light in the north like a match. The world

00:19:12.360 --> 00:19:15.149
was covered

00:19:15.149 --> 00:19:15.159
in

00:19:15.159 --> 00:19:18.870
blackness,

00:19:18.870 --> 00:19:18.880
but

00:19:18.880 --> 00:19:21.110
like

00:19:23.830 --> 00:19:23.840
a

00:19:25.440 --> 00:19:27.909
chick

00:19:29.390 --> 00:19:29.400
breaking

00:19:30.760 --> 00:19:32.390
out of

00:20:53.840 --> 00:20:57.789
an egg,

00:21:20.120 --> 00:21:23.070
the light

00:21:32.760 --> 00:21:36.710
exploded that blackness off.

00:21:36.720 --> 00:21:40.110
It

00:21:41.990 --> 00:21:42.000
shattered

00:21:44.039 --> 00:21:47.190
like ice.

00:21:50.950 --> 00:21:50.960
This

00:21:55.679 --> 00:21:58.830
intense light, similar to

00:21:58.830 --> 00:21:58.840
what is

00:21:58.840 --> 00:22:01.789
at the Father's throne,

00:22:13.279 --> 00:22:17.070
started sending rays of light through

00:22:17.080 --> 00:22:19.269
that

00:22:19.279 --> 00:22:21.750
membrane.

00:22:33.840 --> 00:22:36.549
After I saw all the

00:22:36.549 --> 00:22:36.559
scenes,

00:22:36.559 --> 00:22:41.549
I saw men

00:22:41.559 --> 00:22:46.190
and women of God dressed in

00:22:46.200 --> 00:22:50.149
white. They

00:22:50.149 --> 00:22:50.159
were saturated

00:22:50.159 --> 00:22:53.149
in a

00:22:53.149 --> 00:22:53.159
glow

00:22:53.159 --> 00:22:55.230
like honey.

00:22:55.230 --> 00:22:55.240
The glory

00:22:55.240 --> 00:22:57.190
of the

00:22:57.190 --> 00:22:57.200
Lord

00:22:57.200 --> 00:23:02.070
was

00:23:21.880 --> 00:23:24.909
present on them. The

00:23:24.919 --> 00:23:28.950
Lord said this will be the remnant that

00:23:28.960 --> 00:23:32.190
rises up with a

00:23:32.200 --> 00:23:34.750
supernatural covering. When

00:23:42.440 --> 00:23:45.070
the plague

00:23:45.080 --> 00:23:47.990
tries to get on them, it

00:23:47.990 --> 00:23:48.000
dies

00:23:48.000 --> 00:23:50.710
because of that honey glow.

00:23:50.720 --> 00:23:53.310
The

00:24:06.520 --> 00:24:09.350
glory of the Lord kills it. He said,

00:24:13.600 --> 00:24:17.310
'Son, you will not survive this if you do

00:24:17.320 --> 00:24:20.230
not have an understanding of the

00:24:20.240 --> 00:24:23.870
power of the name of

00:24:23.870 --> 00:24:23.880
Jesus.'The

00:24:23.880 --> 00:24:26.510
people who

00:24:26.520 --> 00:24:29.470
walk in

00:24:29.470 --> 00:24:29.480
this

00:24:29.480 --> 00:24:32.789
will have a revelation of the glory and

00:24:32.799 --> 00:24:35.549
the

00:24:37.799 --> 00:24:40.710
Covenant.

00:24:40.710 --> 00:24:40.720
It

00:24:40.720 --> 00:24:44.029
must

00:24:44.039 --> 00:24:47.389
be a

00:24:47.389 --> 00:24:47.399
Rhema

00:24:47.399 --> 00:24:50.350
word. He said if

00:24:54.110 --> 00:24:54.120
you

00:24:59.000 --> 00:25:01.710
wait until this is

00:25:01.720 --> 00:25:04.710
at your door, it will be

00:25:04.720 --> 00:25:07.630
too late. This is

00:25:07.630 --> 00:25:07.640
a fast

00:25:07.640 --> 00:25:10.750
development you

00:25:10.750 --> 00:25:10.760
must

00:25:10.760 --> 00:25:13.630
take

00:25:19.120 --> 00:25:22.389
seriously.

00:25:28.120 --> 00:25:30.669
You must bring in the

00:25:30.679 --> 00:25:34.149
harvest while it is day, for night is

00:25:34.159 --> 00:25:37.190
coming. The window of opportunity

00:25:38.200 --> 00:25:41.870
is closing.

00:25:43.990 --> 00:25:44.000
Many

00:25:46.880 --> 00:25:48.389
will not learn how

00:25:48.399 --> 00:25:51.070
to stand

00:25:53.080 --> 00:25:55.070
because they

00:25:55.070 --> 00:25:55.080
are

00:25:55.080 --> 00:25:56.350
baby

00:25:56.360 --> 00:25:58.909
Christians,

00:25:58.919 --> 00:26:01.350
but it's vital they

00:26:01.360 --> 00:26:04.950
get born again

00:26:09.799 --> 00:26:13.750
so they don't go to hell.

00:26:17.159 --> 00:26:19.789
Saying the sinner's prayer is everything.

00:26:19.789 --> 00:26:19.799
Our

00:26:19.799 --> 00:26:22.389
ultimate task is to preach that Jesus Christ is coming and to get people

00:26:28.320 --> 00:26:31.830
born again.

00:26:55.000 --> 00:26:58.070
If

00:26:59.880 --> 00:27:02.750
we do not pray to

00:27:02.760 --> 00:27:04.830
lessen this,

00:27:04.840 --> 00:27:07.430
many people

00:27:07.430 --> 00:27:07.440
will

00:27:07.440 --> 00:27:11.389
die and go to hell. This

00:27:11.389 --> 00:27:11.399
is a

00:27:11.399 --> 00:27:16.750
stern

00:27:16.760 --> 00:27:19.789
word, but these people are

00:27:19.799 --> 00:27:22.590
ruthless.

00:27:42.720 --> 00:27:45.669
The Lord told me to

00:27:45.669 --> 00:27:45.679
listen

00:27:45.679 --> 00:27:47.310
to Steve

00:27:47.310 --> 00:27:47.320
Cioccolanti's

00:27:47.320 --> 00:27:50.549
sermon

00:27:50.559 --> 00:27:53.710
about the horses.

00:27:53.720 --> 00:27:56.149
I told

00:27:56.159 --> 00:27:58.549
him

00:27:58.549 --> 00:27:58.559
he

00:27:58.559 --> 00:28:01.149
must preach it more.

00:28:23.240 --> 00:28:26.750
It was a confirmation

00:28:26.760 --> 00:28:28.990
because he heard

00:28:29.000 --> 00:28:30.750
it too.

00:28:32.669 --> 00:28:32.679
The

00:28:35.039 --> 00:28:37.630
Lord

00:28:41.200 --> 00:28:43.149
said many

00:28:43.159 --> 00:28:46.669
prophetic voices have a mixture right

00:28:46.679 --> 00:28:49.389
now; they

00:28:49.399 --> 00:28:51.389
are not hearing the clear word because they are filled

00:28:51.389 --> 00:28:51.399
with the praise of

00:28:51.399 --> 00:28:53.230
man and ego. They

00:28:53.230 --> 00:28:53.240
have 'wax'in their ears.

00:28:53.240 --> 00:28:55.310
They must prophesy from the

00:28:55.320 --> 00:28:57.750
throne room.

00:29:24.600 --> 00:29:27.870
As you

00:30:58.480 --> 00:31:01.549
surrender, He will

00:31:01.559 --> 00:31:04.190
show you what is to come.

00:31:50.679 --> 00:31:53.430
In the last

00:31:53.440 --> 00:31:55.029
days, there will be plagues,

00:31:55.039 --> 00:31:57.389
pestilences,

00:31:59.320 --> 00:32:01.029
and

00:32:04.039 --> 00:32:06.310
famines.

00:32:29.960 --> 00:32:33.310
Do not

00:32:33.320 --> 00:32:38.470
focus on that; focus on the task at hand.

00:32:38.480 --> 00:32:42.190
Bring in the lost

00:32:42.190 --> 00:32:42.200
and

00:32:42.200 --> 00:32:46.110
teach them their Covenant rights

00:32:46.120 --> 00:32:48.310
and the authority of the

00:32:48.320 --> 00:32:50.549
blood of Jesus.

00:33:07.120 --> 00:33:09.870
You

00:33:09.880 --> 00:33:12.310
must teach my people how to call those

00:33:12.320 --> 00:33:14.629
things that be not as though they were,

00:33:14.629 --> 00:33:14.639
and

00:33:14.639 --> 00:33:16.389
that they have power to

00:33:16.399 --> 00:33:18.149
tread on serpents and

00:33:18.159 --> 00:33:20.509
scorpions.

00:33:25.440 --> 00:33:27.950
A thousand shall fall at their side,

00:33:27.960 --> 00:33:30.230
but nothing

00:33:30.240 --> 00:33:32.110
shall come nigh them.

00:33:32.120 --> 00:33:34.629
The

00:33:37.909 --> 00:33:37.919
name

00:33:39.789 --> 00:33:39.799
of

00:33:42.919 --> 00:33:44.509
the

00:33:44.519 --> 00:33:46.389
Lord

00:33:48.950 --> 00:33:48.960
is

00:33:51.789 --> 00:33:51.799
a

00:33:54.919 --> 00:33:57.350
strong tower,

00:34:13.359 --> 00:34:16.510
and the righteous run into it and

00:34:16.520 --> 00:34:19.389
are safe. We must know the power

00:34:23.200 --> 00:34:25.669
of

00:34:30.149 --> 00:34:30.159
communion—that

00:34:37.000 --> 00:34:40.349
we have a covenant with Him.

00:34:49.399 --> 00:34:52.510
His blood cleanses us

00:34:56.599 --> 00:35:00.109
and the same power that raised

00:35:00.119 --> 00:35:03.069
Jesus from the dead dwells

00:35:03.079 --> 00:35:05.109
in

00:35:05.119 --> 00:35:09.109
us.

00:35:09.119 --> 00:35:13.270
As He is, so are we

00:35:13.280 --> 00:35:16.910
in this

00:35:16.920 --> 00:35:23.990
world.

00:36:06.720 --> 00:36:09.630
If He delivered the children of

00:36:09.640 --> 00:36:13.230
Israel from the plagues of Egypt, He will

00:36:13.240 --> 00:36:14.750
deliver

00:36:14.760 --> 00:36:18.270
you. They had

00:36:59.680 --> 00:37:00.910
the

00:37:00.920 --> 00:37:05.069
blood

00:37:05.069 --> 00:37:05.079
on

00:37:07.109 --> 00:37:07.119
the

00:37:07.119 --> 00:37:08.470
doorposts,

00:37:08.480 --> 00:37:11.710
and

00:37:11.720 --> 00:37:15.430
the death angel passed over.

00:37:30.240 --> 00:37:33.150
We have

00:37:33.160 --> 00:37:37.030
the ultimate Lamb, Jesus Christ.

00:37:41.880 --> 00:37:43.790
We

00:37:48.720 --> 00:37:51.950
do not fear

00:37:51.960 --> 00:37:57.550
plagues

00:37:57.560 --> 00:38:01.069
because greater is He that is in us than

00:38:01.079 --> 00:38:03.309
he that is in the

00:38:03.319 --> 00:38:06.630
world.

00:38:55.920 --> 00:38:58.349
Father, I thank You for the

00:38:58.359 --> 00:39:00.270
precious blood and the

00:39:00.280 --> 00:39:03.550
body that was broken for us.

00:39:03.560 --> 00:39:05.950
We

00:39:05.960 --> 00:39:08.030
have authority in the name

00:39:08.040 --> 00:39:10.950
of Jesus.

00:39:12.640 --> 00:39:15.150
Any kind

00:39:15.160 --> 00:39:17.309
of Black Death or pestilence

00:39:17.319 --> 00:39:19.630
must

00:39:22.349 --> 00:39:22.359
bow.

00:39:25.520 --> 00:39:27.829
I

00:39:30.630 --> 00:39:30.640
am

00:39:34.920 --> 00:39:37.150
not afraid of the

00:39:37.160 --> 00:39:39.230
terror by night.

00:39:58.359 --> 00:40:05.190
I have such an

00:40:05.200 --> 00:40:08.349
urgency

00:40:08.359 --> 00:40:39.430
because

00:40:39.440 --> 00:40:46.870
this wicked

00:40:46.880 --> 00:40:49.990
world

00:40:49.990 --> 00:40:50.000
needs

00:40:50.000 --> 00:41:00.470
help.

00:41:20.079 --> 00:41:23.550
We stopped so much during the

00:41:23.560 --> 00:41:26.589
inauguration;

00:41:26.589 --> 00:41:26.599
we

00:41:26.599 --> 00:41:28.750
are

00:41:28.760 --> 00:41:31.309
an army. I bring this to

00:41:31.319 --> 00:41:35.030
you not for fear, but because the

00:41:35.040 --> 00:41:36.710
Lord said some of this

00:41:36.710 --> 00:41:36.720
will

00:41:36.720 --> 00:41:39.870
happen and we

00:41:45.079 --> 00:41:47.870
can lessen

00:41:47.880 --> 00:41:51.710
it.

00:42:09.760 --> 00:42:12.670
We have

00:42:12.680 --> 00:42:14.630
time to prepare; it’s not this

00:42:14.640 --> 00:42:16.870
year.

00:42:16.870 --> 00:42:16.880
This

00:42:16.880 --> 00:42:20.150
will be a year

00:42:20.160 --> 00:42:21.829
of

00:42:21.839 --> 00:42:24.349
acceleration,

00:42:24.359 --> 00:42:25.790
wealth,

00:42:30.910 --> 00:42:30.920
and

00:42:37.400 --> 00:42:40.910
the glory of the Lord.

00:42:47.480 --> 00:42:50.230
Get

00:42:58.400 --> 00:43:01.549
your 'Joseph

00:43:01.549 --> 00:43:01.559
supply'ready

00:43:01.559 --> 00:43:04.870
and

00:43:04.870 --> 00:43:04.880
get

00:43:04.880 --> 00:43:06.870
out of compromise.

00:43:15.640 --> 00:43:19.069
2025,

00:43:21.160 --> 00:43:25.069
2026,

00:43:25.079 --> 00:43:31.190
and

00:43:31.200 --> 00:43:33.670
2027 are a window

00:43:36.520 --> 00:43:40.950
to pray.

00:43:40.960 --> 00:43:44.109
I see things years

00:43:44.109 --> 00:43:44.119
in the

00:43:44.119 --> 00:43:48.910
distance.

00:43:58.800 --> 00:44:02.349
I saw a

00:44:02.359 --> 00:44:05.549
three-month window—March,

00:44:05.549 --> 00:44:05.559
April,

00:44:05.559 --> 00:44:08.589
and May—where

00:44:08.589 --> 00:44:08.599
the

00:44:08.599 --> 00:44:11.349
bulk of the death

00:44:20.359 --> 00:44:21.950
occurred.

00:44:30.960 --> 00:44:33.150
It started

00:44:40.190 --> 00:44:40.200
showing

00:44:46.760 --> 00:44:48.589
on

00:44:48.599 --> 00:44:50.309
the

00:44:56.599 --> 00:44:58.950
news in

00:44:58.950 --> 00:44:58.960
late

00:44:58.960 --> 00:45:00.950
October

00:45:00.950 --> 00:45:00.960
and

00:45:00.960 --> 00:45:04.470
November.

00:45:31.990 --> 00:45:32.000
Let’s

00:45:57.839 --> 00:45:59.390
take communion and pray.

00:46:15.280 --> 00:46:17.630
Father, we

00:46:17.640 --> 00:46:20.510
thank You

00:46:20.520 --> 00:46:22.910
that by

00:46:22.920 --> 00:46:26.030
Your stripes we are healed. No weapon

00:46:26.040 --> 00:46:28.790
formed against us shall prosper.

00:46:34.920 --> 00:46:38.309
We thank You

00:46:46.240 --> 00:46:47.710
for the wealth of the

00:46:47.710 --> 00:46:47.720
sinner

00:46:47.720 --> 00:46:50.270
laid up for the righteous and

00:46:50.270 --> 00:46:50.280
for

00:46:50.280 --> 00:46:53.349
a year of great

00:46:53.359 --> 00:46:55.950
turnaround.

00:46:55.960 --> 00:46:58.790
We

00:47:01.390 --> 00:47:01.400
are

00:47:04.040 --> 00:47:05.630
the

00:47:05.640 --> 00:47:08.510
Josephs of this generation.

00:47:38.640 --> 00:47:40.630
We apply the blood over our houses,

00:47:40.640 --> 00:47:43.230
marriages, and children.

00:47:57.599 --> 00:48:00.390
We call our unsaved loved ones saved

00:48:00.400 --> 00:48:03.270
and

00:48:03.280 --> 00:48:06.670
delivered.

00:48:06.670 --> 00:48:06.680
As

00:48:08.069 --> 00:48:08.079
we

00:48:08.079 --> 00:48:10.270
take

00:48:10.280 --> 00:48:12.470
this

00:48:12.480 --> 00:48:14.349
blood,

00:48:14.349 --> 00:48:14.359
it

00:48:14.359 --> 00:48:16.630
covers

00:48:16.640 --> 00:48:19.150
us from the

00:48:19.160 --> 00:48:21.630
top of our heads to the soles of our feet.

00:48:25.349 --> 00:48:25.359
We

00:48:31.359 --> 00:48:33.230
take

00:48:57.599 --> 00:49:00.309
authority

00:49:21.480 --> 00:49:23.990
over

00:49:52.150 --> 00:49:52.160
every

00:50:22.680 --> 00:50:24.190
demonic spirit

00:50:24.200 --> 00:50:26.710
and

00:50:26.720 --> 00:50:28.630
pestilence.

00:50:35.079 --> 00:50:39.710
We

00:50:43.960 --> 00:50:46.950
petition

00:50:49.150 --> 00:50:49.160
You,

00:50:53.870 --> 00:50:53.880
Lord,

00:50:56.440 --> 00:50:58.870
to

00:51:00.440 --> 00:51:02.670
spare these people

00:51:02.670 --> 00:51:02.680
and

00:51:02.680 --> 00:51:05.990
call forth

00:51:06.000 --> 00:51:08.670
mercy. We

00:51:08.670 --> 00:51:08.680
turn

00:51:08.680 --> 00:51:10.390
this

00:51:10.400 --> 00:51:12.390
ship around

00:51:12.400 --> 00:51:14.069
through intercessory prayer.

00:51:17.839 --> 00:51:20.910
We

00:51:27.839 --> 00:51:29.470
thank You

00:51:29.480 --> 00:51:32.069
